deskutils/mylar includes an RC script:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/mylar

TO START MYLAR ON BOOT:
echo 'mylar_enable="YES"' >> /etc/rc.conf

START MANUALLY:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/mylar start

Once started, visit the following to configure:
http://localhost:8090/

